```

## Conventions

- `setUp` to create fresh instance for each test
- `blocTest` for testing BLoCs (don't test manually)
- `ProviderContainer` for unit testing providers
- `addTearDown(container.dispose)` for cleanup
- Overrides to inject mocks in integration tests
